    "# ── 2.0 Rebuild pools with 11 features ───────────────────────────────────────\n",
    "#\n",
    "# Dropping fundamentals from the standard feature set increases usable rows\n",
    "# because rows are no longer dropped for fundamental NaN values.\n",
